Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,An unidentified flying object is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uranus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune, when the planetary probe robot of Uranus exploded,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we reported about the approach of an unidentified flying object, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry and report it to the Earth! -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This explosion is a fearful challenge for mankind that staked
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,its future on space development,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and in view of the results so far, Atlas is the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Let's organize the Earth defense force and defeat Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's defeat him! Defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy vs. Atlas IX
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mars base of the Earth defense force
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Atom! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me persuade Atlas before we fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Persuade him? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop conquering the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Atlas has already begun his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been a report that several space stations near Jupiter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was also destroyed, making many victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our mission to defeat Atlas as the Earth defense force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you are also a member of this force!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,World's latest fighter that can even fly in space for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best pilots selected from each country!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is you, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, in this standard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We will defeat Atlas for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! My brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was killed by Atlas at the space station near Saturn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my only brother and an excellent scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the head office of the Earth defense force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The PK-3 5th space station between Jupiter and an asteroid was blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercept it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all hear that? It's an order for a sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, why did you start such reckless thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed innocent people and robots at the end of space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,People were looking for me, so I came out for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good opportunity. Let me take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas is your brother, built from the same blueprint as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas and I are brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian! I told you not to tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you get angry, this is one thing I should say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do, now that you know we are brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to side with me? Side with your brother, Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Th, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't expect such thing from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I tried so hard to win you over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because of that so-called connection of brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have already made decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to suppress my personal emotion in order to achieve my big dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! There is no forgiveness even if we were to be brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas and I are brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew that we were brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have found out that we are brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, why are you in such a daze?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas has run away to an asteroid! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Super Omegatrone cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I developed it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It affects Atlas' omega factor and brings in a powerfully destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerfully destructive power?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to revenge my brother's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to return unless I get rid of Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas! Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Let me finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kiri's coming to get you with a tremendous weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm going to run away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just because some strong one appears?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending you are brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase him! Don't lose track of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Several unidentified flying objects are approaching Saturn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: SA 102, Velocity: V0.8
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what Atom saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Captain Kiri also said that it's something we've never seen on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hmm... Then this is an Invader. -Invader?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an alien from an unknown planet, targeting Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the explosions weren't from Atlas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but from that Invader, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, about Atlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what about Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas seems to be my brother, built from the same blueprint as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that true? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Atom's blueprint stolen by someone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, what is this fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister! This is a video from the Mars base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be reconnaissance unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We are currently passing near the Saturn orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The radar has captured something like a command ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a flying object with tremendous mass. Its diameter is about 10 km.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,10 km of diameter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is the main force, then we must have fought only a very little of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-What must have happened? -Perhaps the Invader...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Connection lost from the Mars base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, UN Secretary General.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious flying object finally stated approaching the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are hundreds of reports from all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are trying to hold an emergency conference. Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I'll go back to the force as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, be careful. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Invader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention! We will encounter the enemy in 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We got rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem, Captain Kiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-The Invader is... In the Earth... -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's the Invader! -It's the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,UN building area also started getting attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All leaders of countries, please evacuate underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... It's an unprovoked assault. Stupid alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... My energy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr.Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A kind person brought you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the relief center next to the UN building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We evacuated, but 70% of New York were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar thing has happened all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the Earth defense force and you, we got rid of the advance troop, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what is going to happen to this Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has been decided in the UN.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We are just trying to unite and get over this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Are you all right? I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Captain Kiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But our troop has shrunken to 1/3.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The main Invader force has now entered the Jupiter orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight them tomorrow with our remaining force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, please join us immediately. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But Atom, I think I have misunderstood Atlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time that the main Invader force approaches the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We are like this already only with the advance troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, will mankind be finished for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that to happen! I have made many friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To imagine to not have them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone must be thinking the same thing. That's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no difference between a human being and a robot in its heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! I'll try asking Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If these two brothers work together, the mankind might be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just heard Atom calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Invader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who tried to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kiri, who lost his brother, has also misunderstood something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid humans... Just get destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not stupid. They are all good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends? What friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots and humans can't be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That is... There were people who made fun of me for being a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But now all of them are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no difference between a human being and a robot in its heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, do you really believe so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Atom is fighting so desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are your friends as well! You are my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are my friends? How could that be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand, Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back and tell them to screw themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth defense force is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Having its final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were human, you would have shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are your friends as well! You are my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... There are so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! It's finally time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show the Invader what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is someone like me in the Earth as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Don't turn your eyes to the small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only target is the command ship of the enemy! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the base of the enemy. All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you should stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show what I've really got from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, let's meet again if our fate allows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure your friends would be my friends as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure that you are my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm entrusting the Earth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I survive, I'll go after another planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Livian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to leave; why would you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be with you, Atlas, whether in life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary black clouds that covers the sky of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster Mazev on a leopard appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and started sprinkling snow on our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out that that snow is a scary creature that takes robots' energy away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I get rid of this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Snow Leopard"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.51,0:23:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
